# Account & Data Deletion — Beyond the Stars

**Last updated:** April 20, 2026

We respect your right to control your personal data. This page explains how to delete your Beyond the Stars account and associated data.

## How to Delete Your Account

### Option 1: In-App Deletion (Recommended)
1. Open the Beyond the Stars app
2. Go to **Settings → Account**
3. Tap **Delete Account**
4. Confirm the deletion

Your account will be deleted immediately, and all associated data will be removed from our servers within 30 days.

### Option 2: Email Request
If you can't access the app (e.g., you've uninstalled it), you can request deletion by email:

**Email:** ecec22squared@gmail.com
**Subject line:** `Account Deletion Request — Beyond the Stars`
**Include:** The email address or username associated with your account

We will process your request within 30 days and send you a confirmation.

## What Data Is Deleted

When you delete your account, the following is permanently removed:
- Account information (email, username)
- Character data and saved game progress
- Story history and AI-generated content
- Any support or contact records

## What Data May Be Retained

We may retain limited data where required by law (e.g., financial records for tax purposes) or for fraud prevention. Any retained data is anonymized and not linked to your identity.

